data.description: Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this house offers the very best in contemporary living. With a complete overhaul that includes a host of brand-new appliances, this property is ready to welcome its new owners. The standout feature of this property is the new garage. Whether you're a car enthusiast or simply in need of additional storage, the spacious and organized garage is sure to impress. Beautiful kitchen, new vinyl plank flooring, fresh paint, and great curb appeal! This home is ready to impress! Schedule your private tour today!
